:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 162 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 162 f.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' You two, take this before we fight Furynox.
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 163.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' This is the Lunaumbra Gourd, a sacred vessel made by the Artisanship Commission. The Ten-Lords Commission has made some changes to it to better suppress heliobi. After you fight the puppets controlled by Furynox, make sure you seal their heliobi fragments in here.
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 164.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Also...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll look after Huohuo.
::{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 165.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Her time as a judge has been brief &mdash; she is still inexperienced. Apart from that, please also have mercy on the spiritfarers that have fallen under Furynox's control.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll go easy on the spiritfarers.
::{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 166.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' The Ten Lords will not forget your acts of kindness. Thank you.
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 232.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' Mr. Tail, we're gonna fight some really dangerous enemies now. Please lend me your strength, too.
:{{A|VO side2 hh tail 159.ogg}} '''Tail:''' Oh-ho? Sounds like someone finally learned to talk tough.
:{{A|VO side2 hh tail 160.ogg}} '''Tail:''' I would've believed you if your legs weren't shaking so much!
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 233 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 233 f.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' Don't point that out! It took me a lot of effort to be this brave! All this time I've just been hiding behind {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer). I'm such a bad judge...
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 234.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' Madam Xueyi said those possessed by a heliobus can't get possessed again... I'm the only person who can help everyone!
:{{A|VO side2 hh tail 161.ogg}} '''Tail:''' Exactly! You're welcome, by the way... So, what are we waiting for? Let's go!
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 167.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Huohuo, though I am of ingenium body, I too am feeling a sliver of fear.
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 235.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' Madam Xueyi... you're afraid too?
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 168.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Faced with a demon that can manipulate life at will, of course I'm afraid... Afraid that I won't ever work with my sister again.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Huohuo, I'm afraid too.
::{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 236.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' ...I&mdash;I guess if even you two are afraid, then... I&mdash;I feel a little better now.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Afraid or not, we're still gonna beat the heck out of it!
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 169.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Let's go! I will find my own way to defeat the pawns possessed by Furynox... and before that foolish heliobus has realized what's happening, I will suppress all of their fragments within the Lunaumbra Gourd.
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 237.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' ...So we'll need to activate the Evil Binding Matrix, right?
:{{A|VO side2 hh xueyi 170.ogg}} '''Xueyi:''' Once my task is done, I will meet you at the Verdantia Terrace and activate the Evil Binding Matrix at its matrix core.
:{{A|VO side2 hh huohuo 238.ogg}} '''Huohuo:''' Okay.
